From bd368a5814a5142f42b233cc1c947f0f345c703a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <assistant@local>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 07:21:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add custom cover illustrations for all blog posts

Generated matching SVG illustrations for each post, themed and
color-matched to its existing grad-1..4 gradient:
- smart auto injector: circuit + syringe + ultrasonic waves
- healthcare Java Swing: dashboard + medical cross + coffee cup
- from curiosity to code: winding path + code brackets
- AI as a student developer: neural network + laptop

Wired coverImage into blog.js and used it (with graceful fallback to
the old gradient) in both the blog listing card and the article hero.
